entry.title: CadetEditor/CadetEngine-as
entry.summary: CadetEngine is a component-based AS3 Scene Engine supporting 2D and 3D GPU accelerated rendering, physics, custom behaviours and 3rd party library integration. It has been designed from the ground up to be plug-and-play with editability in mind.
